    Welcome to Variant MediSystems

    Variant Medisystems is a trailblazing supplier of cutting-edge ultrasound equipment, catering to the regions of Visakhapatnam, Vijayanagaram, Srikakulam, Krishna District, East Godavari, and West Godavari. Our inception in 2021 marked the beginning of our commitment to the healthcare sector. As the exclusive distributor for the aforementioned territory in Andhra Pradesh, we have embarked on a mission to deliver unparalleled medical solutions and services.

    Our Products

    E2 is a color Doppler ultrasound system that reaches beyond your expectations due to its compact and fashionable appearance. It fulfills GI, OB/GYN, Cardiac and POC applications to fit your routine scanning needs while its color mode will help you for more accurate and efficient diagnosis of lesions.

    The P10 color Doppler ultrasound system is designed to provide our clinicians with high quality images, abundant probe selection, various clinical tools and automatic analysis software. With the help of P10, a smart and thoughtful experience is created to address growing demand for different clinical applications.

    Incorporating innovative technologies, P20’s user-friendly designed with a simple operation panel, intuitive user interface and a variety of intelligent auxiliary scanning tools, will significantly improve your daily examination experience. Besides general imaging applications, P20 has entitled with diagnostic 4D technology.

    Sono-drop provides a fast and convenient ultrasound image transmission between P40 ELITE and the patients’ smart devices. The bond between clinicians and patients are supposed to be strengthened through more frequent communication. An inspiring tutorial displaying probe placement, anatomy illustration and standard ultrasound image examples.

    Seeing clinicians’ key wants and tasks, S50 ELITE redefines the spectrum of patient care in its segment, especially for OB/GYN applications. To create an easy pathway to exciting ultrasound experience, S50 ELITE provides a delicate combination of outstanding clinical precision, elevated productivity and thoughtful workflow.

    The SonoScape S60 adopts the intelligent Wis+ platform to help ultrasound professionals acquire and interpret ultrasound images more efficiently and precisely. It is a premium system that keeps your practice at the forefront of ultrasound examinations and enables you to provide meticulous care for patients.

    We provide high-quality medical equipment to healthcare providers in Andhra Pradesh, India. Our products are sourced from reputable suppliers globally and meet the highest standards set by the industry. With our range of equipment options, we ensure healthcare providers have access to what they need to deliver quality healthcare services.

    Ensure that your medical equipment is always in top condition with our equipment maintenance services. Our team of experts has the knowledge and skills to provide regular inspections, repairs, and preventative maintenance to prevent any unexpected downtime.
